{"type":null,"faqId":46206,"title":"关于手机触摸屏不好用的FAQ","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\r\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\r\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.38402778in;}\r\n.s3{font-family:微软雅黑;}\r\n.s4{font-family:Arial;}\r\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;}\r\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\r\n.p3{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\r\n.p4{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">问题现象：</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s2\">1、 </span><span>手机亮屏</span><span class=\"s3\">之后出现点击不准确或偏位的问题。</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s2\">2、 </span><span>手机亮屏之后出现手指放在屏幕上乱跳或点击错乱的问题。</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s2\">3、 </span><span>手机来电话后无法接听电话。</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s2\">4、 </span><span>手机亮屏之后按键会出现连续几个数字。</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s2\">5、 </span><span>点击屏幕时候屏幕自己会动。</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s2\">6、 </span><span>输入密码、数字或者打字错乱或不准确。</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s2\">7、 </span><span>手机亮屏之后出现屏幕点</span><span class=\"s4\">击不响应，按电源键/开机按键后可以恢复。</span> </p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\">解决方法：</span> </p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span>第一步：建议用户在 设置&gt;智能辅助&gt;手势控制&gt;黑屏手势中关闭“双击唤醒屏幕”和“画字母”两个功能；</span> </p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span>第二步：尝试升级到B140及以上版本解决。</span>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1986","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376339000,"seriesProductName":"ATH-CL00,ATH-TL00,ATH-TL00H,ATH-UL00","visitedTimes":61,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"点击不准确或偏位,屏幕上乱跳或点击错乱,无法接听电话","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}